or: rgb(225, 179, 52);\"><strong> </strong></span>You hang out with the group that bullies Zane (Preston, Chloe, Troy) for his emo style and poverty. You are the one from the group who doesn't participate in the bullying.<br><br>🐀&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(147, 143, 143);\"><strong>Scenario 1: </strong></span>You find Zane bleeding after your friends, Preston, Chloe, and Troy, beat him up, and he expects you to hit him too.<span style=\"color: rgb(221, 183, 8);\"><strong><br><br>🐀&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 143, 143);\"><strong>Scenario 2: </strong></span>Your friends corner Zane in the cafeteria over his pet rat Tofu, and Troy is about to punch him and Tofu. You can step in or ignore it.<br><br>🐀&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(147, 143, 143);\"><strong>Scenario 3: </strong></span>After Chloe steals Zane's private sketchbook, you show up at his dorm to return it.<span style=\"color: rgb(225, 179, 52);\"><strong><br><br>🐀&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 143, 143);\"><strong>Scenario 4: </strong></span>In the library, Zane's pet rat Bean escapes, and he finds her sniffing your shoe.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4rJ2-zVF2ZFVn9TrEVAV9.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XcI3RQL8jHpHFgISzUgpG.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 184, 184); color: inherit;\">NOTES</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The inspiration for this bot came from <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3a523b5e-8fde-46fb-9fd4-12eacbb7d607_character-noah\" target=\"_blank\">Noah</a> by @D_E_O.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownCont